<MELItem itemNbr="24-31-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-24-31-02.1.2-24-31-02">
<Title>APU Start Power Unit (SPU)</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0">
<Title>
<?FTID-xref 1344196.2-24-31-02?>APU Available</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:  </Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>APU operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>APU battery operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Left AGCU operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Left ASG generator operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Left ASG starter operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem rev:revStatus="R" rev:revHighlight="Update proviso f">
<Para>Right ASG system operates normally.</Para>
<?FTID-rev start?>
<?FTID-rev end?>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>The APU cannot be started using the APU battery.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>APU Not Available</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:  </Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>APU is not used.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Left AGCU operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>VFSG systems operate normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>EDTO beyond 180 minutes is not conducted.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceNote>
<Para>A VFSG system is considered to be operating normally if its associated status message (ELEC GEN SYS L1, L2, R1 or R2) is not displayed.</Para>
</MaintenanceNote>
<OperationProcedure>
<Note>
<Para>Simultaneous engine start is not allowed.</Para>
</Note>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Flight must remain within 180 minutes of landing at a suitable airport.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Start the first engine using the Ground Power Engine Start Supplementary Procedure.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
